  ],
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "content": "（旁⽩）三年前，⾝为朝廷重⾂的外祖⽗被⼈构陷通敌叛国，在狱中蒙冤致死，⽗亲和嫡⺟害",
      "character": "苏锦",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 8.3,
      "scene": "苏府，夜，内",
      "line_num": 6
    },
    {
      "content": "爹，我娘快不⾏了，求求您给我五⼗⽂为娘请个⼤夫。",
      "character": "苏锦",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 6.1,
      "scene": "苏府，夜，内",
      "line_num": 10
    },
    {
      "content": "⽗亲，你宁可给狗治病，也不愿救我娘亲性命么！\u0001",
      "character": "苏锦",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 6.3,
      "scene": "苏府，夜，内",
      "line_num": 17
    },
    {
      "content": "⼤胆！还不快滚！别在这冲撞了神医！",
      "character": "苏承",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 6.2,
      "scene": "苏府，夜，内",
      "line_num": 18
    },
    {
      "content": "娘，⼥⼉没⽤。没能求到半⽂钱，明天我就去清⽉楼求求⽼妈妈，借些钱给您买药。",
      "character": "苏锦",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 9.8,
      "scene": "、林场，夜，内",
      "line_num": 24
    },
    {
      "content": "你们要做什么？",
      "character": "苏锦",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 2.4,
      "scene": "、林场，夜，内",
      "line_num": 31
    },
    {
      "content": "（恐惧）⺟亲，我们真的要这样做吗？",
      "character": "苏媚",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 4.4,
      "scene": "、林场，夜，内",
      "line_num": 33
    },
    {
      "content": "⽗亲！我亦是你亲⽣⻣⾁啊！",
      "character": "苏锦",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 3.8,
      "scene": "、林场，夜，内",
      "line_num": 37
    },
    {
      "content": "夫⼈，我觉得不妥。",
      "character": "苏承",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 3.1,
      "scene": "、林场，夜，内",
      "line_num": 38
    },
    {
      "content": "锦⼉的脸蛋实在太美了，趁早砸烂得好，否则到了阴曹地府，若是被达官贵⼈给看上，到时候",
      "character": "苏承",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 10.2,
      "scene": "、林场，夜，内",
      "line_num": 40
    },
    {
      "content": "毒妇，我就算做⻤，也不会放过你们！",
      "character": "苏锦",
      "emotion": null,
      "emotional_direction": null,
      "speed_type": "normal",
      "duration": 5.2,
      "scene": "、林场，夜，内",
      "line_num": 43
    }
  ],
